{"tid":547291,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram悄悄從App Store下架 真相係.....","createTime":"2018-02-01T10:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T04:11:44.000Z","uid":2474,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"89f75d4d78f5b6fcf4e7736b48533053967dc00d","tid":547291,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"Telegram for iOS及其用Swift編寫的最新版Telegram X，突然從App Store消失。原本以為只在香港和大陸的App Store消失，但其實全球用家都下載不到。最奇怪的，是在iOS版下架的時候，Android新版本同時推出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，是因為有Telegram程式設計人員，錯手把iOS版下架。官方已知道有關情況，並指會盡快修復有關問題。大家也不用太緊張是不是被人河蟹了等情況。<br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/02/telegram-for-ios-disappeared-from-appstore/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F02%2Ftelegram-for-ios-disappeared-from-appstore%2F&d=6skEbpnF%2FXtZDxY%2F7yju5Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=77a3ae2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/02/telegram-for-ios-disappeared-from-appstore/</a>"},{"pid":"b7a9f66532177f4db3d0497f2c319094a19d9fb9","tid":547291,"uid":1130,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7aa1e44549509bb8a7d17c7dca5f8bb4759a18","tid":547291,"uid":151490,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bec7ef64674fc92e5946ff5f8a33c3b469c6354","tid":547291,"uid":28558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母標題黨"},{"pid":"22595270c5edd78673fcba0f16dedb5635cbb867","tid":547291,"uid":3223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d0e6a4a8b05991a06cecb21